IMF Says Zimbabwe’s Economic Recovery Welcome, Though It Faces Challenges

-- B y   T i m   S m i t h
-- 
2011-06-09T21:10:03Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-09/imf-says-zimbabwe-s-economic-recovery-welcome-though-it-faces-challenges.html
International Monetary Fund
Executive Directors say they welcome  Zimbabwe ’s economic
recovery and warned it remains fragile and is facing challenges.
They made the comments in an Article IV consultation published
on their website.  To contact the reporter on this story:
